{"comments":"Mesh2D color sampling and interpolation functions.\n\n## Barycentric Interpolation\n\n- `barycentricWeights`: Compute barycentric coordinates for a point in a triangle\n- `interpolateColor`: Interpolate RGB colors using barycentric weights\n\n## Triangle Sampling\n\n- `sampleTriangleAt`: Sample color at a point within a triangle\n- `findAndSampleTriangle`: Find containing triangle and sample\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Barycentric weights for a point within a triangle.\n\nWeights sum to 1.0 for points inside the triangle.\nNegative weights indicate the point is outside.\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["u",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["v",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["w",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[75,68],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Mesh2D/Sampling.purs","start":[75,1]},"title":"BarycentricWeights"},{"children":[],"comments":"Compute barycentric weights for a point in a triangle.\n\nGiven a point P and triangle vertices A, B, C, computes weights\nsuch that P = u*A + v*B + w*C (where u + v + w = 1).\n\nIf any weight is negative, the point is outside the triangle.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Point"],"Point2D"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Pri